{
  "stem": "3165.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And-- and this woman, she recognized me, or she knew that I, you know, was a Jewish kid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And two guys walked into the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "They weren't dressed in uniforms, but they were Ukrainian guys that were supporting the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And this woman-- they came in, they saw me, and the woman says, there's-- this one is a [UKRAINIAN], which means a Jewish kid.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] And so the-- well, these two guys, they said, oh, well, we've got to take her to the police, to the Ukrainian police, which are like the Germans, you know, working together.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And it was late at night, and we walked out, and one guy was in front of me, and I was in the middle, and the second guy was behind me, walking to the police station or police house, to the-- this head policeman house.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And I thought to myself, well, now-- now only my sister is going to be left alone, my youngest sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And I was walking, and somehow, I remember I wasn't so scared, because I thought, well, God is with me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "God is with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "[SOBS] And we walked, and sure enough, they took me right into this policeman's house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was like an office in the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "And I walked in, and sure enough, he-- he was sitting, this head Gestapo or Ukrainian, was sitting at the table, and a lot of other policeman around the table.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And bottles of liquor were on the table.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And I could see that he was drunk, or he was drinking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "I don't think I knew what drunk meant, but I saw he was drinking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And-- but he didn't have his hat on, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
